1. How can we make n no of divs of same size for any amount of content /
Ans -
<style>
.col-container {
  display: table;
  width: 100%;
}
.col {
  display: table-cell;
  padding: 16px;
}
</style>
<div class="col-container">
  <div class="col" style="background:orange">
    <p>Hello World</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col" style="background:yellow">
    <h2>Column 2</h2>
    <p>Hello World!</p>
    <p>Hello World!</p>
    <p>Hello World!</p>
    <p>Hello World!</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col" style="background:orange">
    <h2>Column 3</h2>
    <p>Some other text..</p>
  </div>
</div>
--------Another Way --------
<style>
.col-container  {
  width:100%;
  height:auto;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:row;
  justify-content:space-around;
  flex-flow:wrap;
}
.col {
  width:25%;
  height:200px;
  margin:10px;
  box-size:border-box;
}
</style>
