12. what will be the output if we use multiple return in one render ?
Ans -
class App extends React.Component {
  render() {
    return (<div>Morning</div>)
    return (<div>Noon</div>)
    return (<div>Evening</div>)
  }
}
React.render(<App />, document.getElementById('app')); // Morning
